# 1D Acoustic Wave problem

REQUIRES Driver
REQUIRES physics/Eos/EosMain/Gamma
REQUIRES physics/Hydro

D sim_amp Amplitude of the perturbation wave
PARAMETER sim_amp     REAL 1.e-6               [0 to ]

D sim_gamma Ratio of specific heats for gas
PARAMETER sim_gamma   REAL 1.6666666666666667  [0.0 to ] 

D sim_rho Initial mass density
PARAMETER sim_rho     REAL 1.                  [0 to ]

D sim_P Initial pressure
PARAMETER sim_P       REAL 0.6                 [0 to ]

D sim_v Initial velocity in the x-direction
PARAMETER sim_vx      REAL 0.

D sim_e Initial energy
PARAMETER sim_e       REAL 0.9                 [0 to ]

D sim_cs Initial sound speed
PARAMETER sim_cs      REAL 1.

D sim_wavedir Sign of the velocity of the waveform
PARAMETER sim_wavedir REAL 1.

D sim_length Length of the computational domain in the x-direction
PARAMETER sim_lengthx REAL 1.                  [0 to ]

USESETUPVARS StaticHyArrays
IF StaticHyArrays
   LINKIF Hydro_data.F90.staticArrays               physics/Hydro/HydroMain/unsplit
   LINKIF hy_computeFluxes_fluxbuf.F90.staticArrays physics/Hydro/HydroMain/unsplit
   LINKIF hy_computeFluxes.F90.staticArrays         physics/Hydro/HydroMain/unsplit/levelFlux
   LINKIF hy_getRiemannState.F90.staticArrays       physics/Hydro/HydroMain/unsplit
ENDIF


